@startwbs
title FreshFood AI - Functional Decomposition (As-Is)
skinparam shadowing false

* F0 FreshFood AI Platform
** F1 Khach hang
*** Dang ky, dang nhap, quan ly tai khoan
*** Xem/tim loc san pham va xem chi tiet
*** Gio hang, dat hang, theo doi don, sua/huy don cho xac nhan
*** AI Scanner (camera/upload) va gui feedback ket qua
*** Chatbot goi n8n + goi y san pham

** F2 Quan tri he thong
*** Dashboard thong ke tong quan
*** Quan ly nguoi dung (xem, doi vai tro, xoa)
*** Quan ly san pham (them, sua, an/xoa mem, upload anh)
*** Quan ly don hang (xem, cap nhat trang thai, xoa)

** F3 API Backend
*** Auth APIs: /api/auth/*
*** Product APIs: /api/products/* + review
*** Order APIs: /api/orders/* + luong admin
*** Scan APIs: /api/scans/* + quick-analyze + feedback

** F4 Du lieu va luu tru
*** CSDL SQLAlchemy (SQLite/PostgreSQL)
*** Thu muc uploads (products, scans)
*** Khoi tao bang va bo sung cot metadata san pham

** F5 Van hanh va chat luong
*** Health check, validation handler
*** Observability: /metrics (request + scan metrics)
*** CI/CD: test backend, build frontend, build/push Docker images
*** Train model MobileNetV2 + xuat labels cho frontend

@endwbs
